        </nav>

        <!-- Calculator -->
        <section class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md" aria-labelledby="calc-title">
          <h1 id="calc-title" class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2 text-slate-800">Mortgage Refinance Calculator</h1>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Estimate your new payment, monthly savings, <strong>break-even time</strong>, and total interest saved when refinancing your current mortgage.</p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <label for="currentBalance" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800">Current remaining balance *</label>
              <div class="relative">
                <input id="currentBalance" type="number" inputmode="decimal" step="0.01" min="0" placeholder="e.g., 280000"
                       class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
                       aria-describedby="balHint balErr" aria-required="true">
                <span class="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-400">$</span>
              </div>
              <p id="balHint" class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Principal only; exclude escrow or fees.</p>
              <p id="balErr" class="text-xs text-red-600 min-h-[1rem]" role="alert" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="currentRate" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800">Current APR (%) *</label>
              <div class="relative">
                <input id="currentRate" type="number" inputmode="decimal" step="0.001" min="0" max="100" placeholder="e.g., 5.75"
                       class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
                       aria-describedby="crErr" aria-required="true">
                <span class="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-400">%</span>
              </div>
              <p id="crErr" class="text-xs text-red-600 min-h-[1rem]" role="alert" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-2">
              <label for="monthsRemaining" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800">Months remaining *</label>
              <input id="monthsRemaining" type="number" inputmode="numeric" step="1" min="1" placeholder="e.g., 300"
                     class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
                     aria-describedby="mrErr" aria-required="true">
              <p id="mrErr" class="text-xs text-red-600 min-h-[1rem]" role="alert" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="newRate" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800">New APR (%) *</label>
              <div class="relative">
                <input id="newRate" type="number" inputmode="decimal" step="0.001" min="0" max="100" placeholder="e.g., 6.00"
                       class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
                       aria-describedby="nrErr" aria-required="true">
                <span class="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-400">%</span>
              </div>
              <p id="nrErr" class="text-xs text-red-600 min-h-[1rem]" role="alert" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="newTermYears" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800">New term (years) *</label>
              <input id="newTermYears" type="number" inputmode="numeric" step="1" min="1" value="30"
                     class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
                     aria-describedby="ntErr" aria-required="true">
              <p id="ntErr" class="text-xs text-red-600 min-h-[1rem]" role="alert" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-2">
              <label for="pointsCosts" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800">Points + closing costs (financed)</label>
              <div class="relative">
                <input id="pointsCosts" type="number" inputmode="decimal" step="0.01" min="0" placeholder="e.g., 3500"
                       class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
                       aria-describedby="pcHint pcErr">
                <span class="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-400">$</span>
              </div>
              <p id="pcHint" class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Assumes costs are added to the new principal (financed). Set to 0 if paying cash at closing.</p>
              <p id="pcErr" class="text-xs text-red-600 min-h-[1rem]" role="alert" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Actions -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-4">
            <button id="calcBtn" type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[44px] px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Calculate</button>
            <button id="resetBtn" type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[44px] px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-blue-600 text-blue-700 font-semibold hover:bg-blue-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Reset</button>
          </div>

          <!-- Results -->
          <div id="results" class="mt-8 bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Results</h2>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
              <div class="bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-lg p-4"><p class="text-sm text-gray-600">New payment (P&amp;I)</p><p id="newPay" class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-blue-700 mt-1">$0</p></div>
              <div class="bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-lg p-4"><p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Monthly savings</p><p id="monthlySave" class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-emerald-700 mt-1">$0</p></div>
              <div class="bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-lg p-4"><p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Break-even time</p><p id="breakeven" class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 mt-1">—</p></div>
              <div class="bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-lg p-4"><p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Interest saved</p><p id="interestSave" class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-emerald-700 mt-1">$0</p></div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4">
              <div class="bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-lg p-4"><p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Current payment (est.)</p><p id="currPay" class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 mt-1">$0</p></div>
              <div class="bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-lg p-4"><p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Costs financed</p><p id="costsOut" class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 mt-1">$0</p></div>
              <div class="bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-lg p-4"><p class="text-sm text-gray-600">New payment (echo)</p><p id="piOut" class="text-xl font-extrabold text-blue-700 mt-1">$0</p></div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-3">Assumes fixed rate, monthly compounding, and on-time payments. Escrow (taxes/insurance) and prepayment penalties are excluded.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SEO content (kept & polished) -->
        <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md mt-8 prose">
          <h2>Methodology &amp; Formulas</h2>
          <div class="formula" aria-label="Refinance formulas">
            Monthly rate: \( i = \text{APR}/100/12 \) &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp; Payment over \( n \) months: \( M = L \cdot \dfrac{i}{1-(1+i)^{-n}} \) (for \( i&gt;0 \)); if \( i=0 \), \( M=L/n \).<br/>
            <strong>Current loan (remaining \(n_\text{rem}\) months)</strong>: \( M_\text{curr} = M(L_\text{rem}, i_\text{curr}, n_\text{rem}) \).<br/>
            <strong>New loan</strong> with financed costs \( C \): principal \( L_\text{new} = L_\text{rem} + C \); term \( n_\text{new} = 12 \cdot \text{years} \); payment \( M_\text{new} = M(L_\text{new}, i_\text{new}, n_\text{new}) \).<br/>
            <strong>Monthly savings</strong>: \( S = \max(M_\text{curr} - M_\text{new}, 0) \).<br/>
            <strong>Break-even (months)</strong>: \( \text{BE} = C / S \) (undefined if \( S=0 \)).<br/>
            <strong>Interest saved (approx.)</strong>: \( I_\Delta \approx (M_\text{curr} \cdot n_\text{rem} - L_\text{rem}) - (M_\text{new} \cdot n_\text{new} - L_\text{new}) \).
          </div>

          <h2>Practical Notes</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Costs financed vs. paid at closing:</strong> Financing increases the new principal and slightly reduces savings; paying cash keeps principal lower.</li>
            <li><strong>Shorter terms save more interest:</strong> A 15–20 year refi often cuts lifetime interest dramatically versus a 30-year reset.</li>
            <li><strong>Lender methods vary:</strong> Posting dates, daily accrual, rounding, and fees can cause small deviations from this idealized model.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>FAQs</h2>
          <h3>Is a small rate drop still worth it?</h3>
          <p>It can be if costs are low or you’re shortening the term. Focus on <em>break-even months</em> and total interest saved.</p>
          <h3>What about prepayment penalties?</h3>
          <p>Some loans carry penalties; this tool doesn’t include them. Review your note and lender’s payoff statement.</p>

          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 border-t pt-4">
            Tool developed by <strong>Ugo Candido</strong>. Content verified by the <strong>CalcDomain Editorial Team</strong>.<br/>
            Last reviewed: October 9, 2025.
          </div>
        </article>
      </main>

      <!-- Right: Sidebar -->
      <aside class="w-full lg:w-1/3">
